text: These kings are of the Picts from the year 822 BC until 312 CE, these monarchs are legendary especially seen with Gil Gidi who ruled for 150 years which is impossible. All of these are legendary. For real kings of the Picts see List of Pictish kings which continues this list from 312 AD. == Before Christ (BC) == * Circin 822-782 BC * Fidach 782-742 BC * Floclaid 742-712 BC * Got 712-700 BC * Ce 700-685 BC * Fibaid 685-661 BC * Gede-olgudach 661-581 BC * Denbecan 581-481 BC * Oflinecta 481-421 BC * Guidid-gaed-brechach 421-371 BC * Gest- gurgich 371-331 BC * Wurgest 331-301 BC * Gilgidi 331-181 BC * Tharain 181-81 BC * Morleo 81-66 BC * Deocliunon 66-26 BC * Cimoiod 26-19 BC * Deoord 19 BC-31 AD == Anno Domini (AD) == * Deoord 19 BC-31 AD * Bliesblituth 31-36 AD * Dectotric 36-76 AD * Usconbuts 76-106 AD * Carvost 106-126 AD * Deo Ardivois 126-146 AD * Vist 146-196 AD * Ru 196-296 AD * Gartnait Ioc 296-305 AD * Breth 305-312 AD == References == Category:Lists of British monarchs Category:Kings and Queens of Scotland
title: List of legendary Pictish monarchs
